类 IGtPush

java.lang.Object
  com.gexin.rp.sdk.http.IGtPush
所有已实现的接口：
IGtAlias, IGtAPN, IIGtPush, IIGtQuery
public class IGtPush
extends java.lang.Object
implements IIGtPush, IIGtQuery, IGtAPN, IGtAlias

This class implements the IIGtPush interface, it contains all functions for pushing. It's thread safety, so you can share the same instance between different thread. In fact we recommand you share the same instance, to save the resource of the programme.

pushMessageToList

public void pushMessageToList(ListMessage message,
                              com.gexin.rp.sdk.base.IListProvider listProvider,
                              com.gexin.rp.sdk.base.IPushEventListener listener)
从接口 IIGtPush 复制的描述
推送消息到一组用户，该方法先从listProvider的实现类中获得一批用户。 然后发送到个推上，每推送完一批就再次从listProvider中获得一批用户。 直到，listProvider不再返回任何用户。 同时每发送一次，就会触发IPushEventListener的事件可以实现该接口获得发送的结果信息
Push messages to a group of users, this method gets a bunch of users in listProvider type and then send to Getui, each time it finishes it reload another bunch of users from listProvider until no new user is returned by listProvider. Each time it sends, the IPushEventListener event will be triggered thus get the sent message result.

指定者：
接口 IIGtPush 中的 pushMessageToList
参数：
message - 推送消息
message for push
listProvider - 列表提供类
Type:list provider
listener - 推送结果监听类
Type:Listener of push result

After you got Content ID though IIGtPush.getContentId(ListMessage message) interface, you can push message to a group of users in targetList.And the length of targetList should less then 50, if you want to push more than 50 users, you should call this method iteratively.

stop

public boolean stop(java.lang.String contentId)
从接口 IIGtPush 复制的描述
停止某次任务，以ContentID作为标识 通过这个方法，可以取消正在发送中的某次任务， 服务器会抛弃所有正在推送中该任务的所有消息， 以及这个任务相关的离线消息，但是已经下发到 手机的消息就无法再收回了。
stop the task according the contentId you can cancel the task in the server through this method. You cannot stop the job if the message have sent to the user's phone.

指定者：
接口 IIGtPush 中的 stop
参数：
contentId - 内容ID
the content id of message tasks
返回：
是否成功停止
stop successful or not

getPushResult

public IPushResult getPushResult(java.lang.String taskId)
从接口 IIGtQuery 复制的描述
获取推送任务编号为指定taskId的推送结果数据。(如：发送数，点击数，接受数等)
Get the details of push result (Such as how many sent, how many user clicked, and how many feedback). only offer toList and toApp tasks, single message is not support.

指定者：
接口 IIGtQuery 中的 getPushResult
参数：
taskId - 任务ID
返回：
The push result contains:
  • result - ok or failed
  • msgTotal - the count of message sent
  • msgProcess - the count of feedback
